.SH NAME
.PP
tollgate-config-set - Set a configuration value


.SH SYNOPSIS
.PP
\fBtollgate config set [key] [value] [flags]\fP


.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
Set a configuration value by dot-path key. Changes are persisted immediately.
Examples:
  tollgate config set metric milliseconds
  tollgate config set step_size 44040192
  tollgate config set accepted_mints.0.price_per_step 2
  tollgate config set show_setup false


.SH OPTIONS
.PP
\fB-h\fP, \fB--help\fP[=false]
	help for set


